{"tid":1888584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上流寄生族涉抄襲印度電影？製片指橋段倒模　勢以牙還牙提告","createTime":"2020-02-20T09:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T17:26:48.000Z","uid":224066,"like":14,"dislike":265,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2635dbf75ade75ee8237b00d5b47ea6c975fbf","tid":1888584,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4028552/org/b87e8ea525ad20d468574069163a0fc9.jpg/aNKjyK7-Yh7ywRcMJtjk0EB-ZJa8Xu_lb4SHKG-Ehyg?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4028552%2Forg%2Fb87e8ea525ad20d468574069163a0fc9.jpg%2FaNKjyK7-Yh7ywRcMJtjk0EB-ZJa8Xu_lb4SHKG-Ehyg%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=15a4aefc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓電影《上流寄生族》在奧斯卡上勇奪4項大獎，導演奉俊昊被譽為「南韓之光」，也成功讓這部電影再次受到大眾討論。印度製片人P. L.德納潘（Thenappan）卻指控《上》片是抄襲1999年他製作的電影《Minsara Kanna》，將會聘請國際律師提出訴訟。<br />\n<br />\nP. L.德納潘接受印度媒體訪問時表示，《上流寄生族》的劇情和自己在1999年製作的電影《Minsara Kanna》極為雷同，接下來將會聘請國際律師提出控告，並且會索取賠償。他不滿過去許多印度片被其他國家的電影控告抄襲，這次只是要「以牙還牙」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4028516/org/16daf4220601a41a49583af65c462026.jpg/A9fZTCg_nvUmurE4XEApwa_8nzR8X3ouXarDPV2qwz0?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4028516%2Forg%2F16daf4220601a41a49583af65c462026.jpg%2FA9fZTCg_nvUmurE4XEApwa_8nzR8X3ouXarDPV2qwz0%3Fv%3Dw640&h=9fb26fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不只如此，就連《Minsara Kanna》電影男主角都認為有抄襲之嫌。而該片導演卻抱持不同看法，直言《上》片雖然有抄襲之嫌，但若《Minsara Kanna》因此而引起國際舞台的關注，就能讓更多人能知道這部電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4028518/org/422462d6f255c9bb38c2cfd1fc15304e.jpg/Z1Gom83YruuE31wMpDFrFIYivN2hZKcyz5hx68-Yces?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4028518%2Forg%2F422462d6f255c9bb38c2cfd1fc15304e.jpg%2FZ1Gom83YruuE31wMpDFrFIYivN2hZKcyz5hx68-Yces%3Fv%3Dw640&h=d628ce6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Minsara Kanna》劇情講述一個有錢太太因為討厭男人，公司所有職員都是女生，男主角因為愛上她，用盡辦法成功當上了她的司機兼保鑣，最後還把弟弟和姊姊都安排進家裡工作的故事，屬於浪漫喜劇片。對於抄襲指控，《上流寄生族》的電影公司CJ娛樂則表示還沒有收到相關信函。"},{"pid":"32e03f77b6357de1edde336b52074a82ff147e4b","tid":1888584,"uid":4574,"like":190,"dislike":4,"score":186,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"印度點拍<br />\n<br />\n賤民點取代派羅門？"},{"pid":"aecfeae874add86f36e9acef61a3d40240be5e54","tid":1888584,"uid":224561,"like":147,"dislike":1,"score":146,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"片中有冇跳舞?"},{"pid":"40dc93218efe6d60f4438ad94fe3584a2d4adacc","tid":1888584,"uid":165749,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"突然間諗起秋香姐果個橋段"},{"pid":"fa63980e57398838b484e1064fff5f7db7d64a06","tid":1888584,"uid":207005,"like":66,"dislike":3,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:24:59.000Z","msg":"印度佬衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1e1df4ba22e03651ad5d1296279ead466aad6e","tid":1888584,"uid":15826,"like":81,"dislike":84,"score":-3,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:26:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 咖哩賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強姦你就叻 識閪電影咩"},{"pid":"22571af07bfd6d240c545378a3debdeed95a6935","tid":1888584,"uid":8014,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"咖哩狗你係咁撚勁就拎左奧斯卡啦"},{"pid":"d95e2104172ddeb53201c2e2d4d30a1b2342b234","tid":1888584,"uid":24044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40dc93218efe6d60f4438ad94fe3584a2d4adacc","tid":1888584,"uid":165749,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"突然間諗起秋香姐果個橋段"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"你啱"},{"pid":"f72dc2145014c1c5bbf053c047149cf385f206a1","tid":1888584,"uid":41343,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://yout